milestones.description: Rameez Shahzad and Adnan Mufti's 75-run partnership is UAE's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 56 between Shaiman Anwar and Haider
Berrington has broken the record for most sixes (23) in ODIs for SCOT, going past Kyle Coetzer's 21
This is the highest match aggregate (599) involving teams U.A.E. & Scotland in ODIs
Rohan Mustafa has broken the record for most catches (10) in ODIs for UAE, going past Ahmed Raza's 9
Kyle Coetzer has scored 14 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for SCOT breaking Fraser Watts's record
Naveed has broken the record for most sixes (12) in ODIs for UAE, going past Shaiman Anwar's 12
